{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/seed-rs/awesome-seed-rs/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7d15aafb-c011-5d67-b74d-3df05f19b554","html":"<!--lint disable double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<h1 id=\"awesome-seed-rs-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-seed-rs-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome seed rs awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Seed RS <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://seed-rs.org/\">\n        <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/seed-rs/seed-rs.org/81ed1acc77062ede3295683f21f2d39611843192/seed_branding/seed_logo.min.svg\" width=\"256\" title=\"Seed logo\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated list of awesome things related to Seed</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://seed-rs.org/\">Seed</a> is an open-source Rust framework for creating fast and reliable web apps running in WebAssembly.</p>\n<p>Contributions welcome. Add links through pull requests or create an issue to start a discussion.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#official-resources\">Official Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#books\">Books</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#quickstarts\">Quickstarts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#bundlers\">Bundlers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#projects-using-seed\">Projects Using Seed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contribute\">Contribute</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"official-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#official-resources\" aria-label=\"official resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Official Resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://seed-rs.org/\">Homepage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed\">GitHub repo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.9k</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://seed.discourse.group\">Forum</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/JHHcHp5\">Chat</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"books\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#books\" aria-label=\"books permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Books</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://erwabook.com/\">Engineering Rust Web Applications</a> - Diesel, Rocket and Seed.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://slowtec.de/posts/2019-12-20-porting-javascript-to-rust-part-1.html\">Porting a JS app to Rust</a> - Porting a JavaScript App to WebAssembly with Rust (blog series).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"quickstarts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quickstarts\" aria-label=\"quickstarts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quickstarts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-quickstart\">Default quickstart</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-quickstart\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">63</span></span></a> - Contains only Rust libraries.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-quickstart-webpack\">Quickstart with Webpack</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-quickstart-webpack\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">78</span></span></a> - Main features: Auto-reload, Prerendering, Minification, <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/\">TailwindCSS</a>, Typescript.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"bundlers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bundlers\" aria-label=\"bundlers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bundlers</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/thedodd/trunk\">Trunk</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/thedodd/trunk\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">467</span></span></a> - WASM web application bundler for Rust.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/panoptix-za/web-bundler\">Web Bundler</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/panoptix-za/web-bundler\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8</span></span></a> - Bundles a Seed SPA for publishing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/seeder\">Seeder</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/seeder\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">36</span></span></a> - Set up Seed app and start dev server by running one command.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-rs-realworld\">RealWorld example</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-rs-realworld\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">82</span></span></a> - \"The mother of all demo apps\" — Exemplary fullstack <a href=\"https://medium.com/\">Medium.com</a> clone.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/seed-realworld-darklang\">Dark lang Realworld</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/seed-realworld-darklang\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</span></span></a> - Seed Realworld example on <em>Quickstart with Webpack</em> with integrated <a href=\"https://darklang.com/\">Dark lang</a> Realworld.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed/tree/master/examples\">Official examples</a> - Smaller examples included in official repo.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/erwa_mytodo\">ERWA mytodo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/erwa_mytodo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">9</span></span></a> - Rust full-stack example. Diesel, Rocket, Seed.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/liketechnik/local-gui-seed-gotham\">Template for GUIs with seed+gotham</a> - Electron like template for local/desktop GUIs with Gotham, rust-embed, web-view and Seed.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/arn-the-long-beard/seeded_game_of_life\">Seeded Game of Life</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/arn-the-long-beard/seeded_game_of_life\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - Game of life with <a href=\"https://dev.to/arnthelongbeard/how-to-only-rust-for-web-frontend-1026\">tutorial</a> in pure Rust inspired by <a href=\"https://rustwasm.github.io/docs/book/\">wasm tutorial</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/warycat/dotawasm\">Dota Underlord Perfect Build</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/warycat/dotawasm\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - An app to help build optimal deck in Dota Underlord.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ide.play-seed.dev\">Play Seed</a> - Playground with several default examples.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"projects-using-seed\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#projects-using-seed\" aria-label=\"projects using seed permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Projects Using Seed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/adexnetwork/adex-explorer\">AdEx Explorer</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/adexnetwork/adex-explorer\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - Shows curated information about the payment channel network of the AdEx advertising protocol.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/kavik.cz\">Kavik.cz</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/MartinKavik/kavik.cz\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - Open-source personal website.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/AlterionX/benxu-dev\">benxu.dev/blog</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/AlterionX/benxu-dev\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - A relatively simple open source personal blog. Built on <a href=\"https://seed-rs.org/\"><code class=\"language-text\">Seed</code></a>, <a href=\"https://maud.lambda.xyz\"><code class=\"language-text\">maud</code></a>, <a href=\"https://rocket.rs\"><code class=\"language-text\">Rocket</code></a>, and <a href=\"https://diesel.rs\"><code class=\"language-text\">Diesel</code></a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-rs.org\">seed-rs.org</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seed-rs/seed-rs.org\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10</span></span></a> - Seed's official website.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/mkroehnert/weightrs\">WeightRS</a> - Minimalistic and privacy friendly progressive web app for tracking your weight.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ethanboxx/planters-rdconf-hackathon-project\">Music composer</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ethanboxx/planters-rdconf-hackathon-project\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - A basic music composition app.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play-seed.dev\">Play Seed</a> - Website about Play Seed, playground to demo Seed apps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://typesync.rutrum.net\">Typesync</a> - Test your typing speed on song lyrics.  Uses <a href=\"https://seed-rs.org/\"><code class=\"language-text\">Seed</code></a>, <a href=\"https://rocket.rs\"><code class=\"language-text\">Rocket</code></a>, and <a href=\"https://diesel.rs\"><code class=\"language-text\">Diesel</code></a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://divykj.github.io/CalcuPi\">CalcuPi</a> - A beautiful Monte Carlo simulation for approximating the value of pi.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.fosskers.ca/en/tools/love-letter\">Love Letter Tracker</a> - A knowledge tracker for the card game <em>Love Letter</em>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whatlang.org/\">Whatlang.org</a> - An interactive demo for whatlang (language recognition library).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"libraries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#libraries\" aria-label=\"libraries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Libraries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/MAlrusayni/savory\">Savory</a> - Library for building user interface based on Seed.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/seed-icons\">seed-icons</a> - Library with collections of icons to include in Seed-based application.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/panoptix-za/seed-bootstrap\">Seed Bootstrap</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/panoptix-za/seed-bootstrap\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"paddin